          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #52525b; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Moles need surface or shallow tunnel traps — the scissor-jaw or harpoon style.</p>
          <a href="https://amzn.to/4lr3Al6" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener">Shop Mole Traps on Amazon</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><a href="/methods" style="color: #047857; font-weight: bold;">Browse all gopher control methods →</a></p>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
